            "html": "<strong>3. Step 3: Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.</strong><div class='step-images count-8'><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FPM/QF5G/KYK4O7UO/FPMQF5GKYK4O7UO.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FS2/74M0/KYK4O7UW/FS274M0KYK4O7UW.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FHZ/I4HX/KYK4O7UX/FHZI4HXKYK4O7UX.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FGU/86NS/KYK4O7UT/FGU86NSKYK4O7UT.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FPM/QF5G/KYK4O7UO/FPMQF5GKYK4O7UO.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FS2/74M0/KYK4O7UW/FS274M0KYK4O7UW.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FHZ/I4HX/KYK4O7UX/FHZI4HXKYK4O7UX.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FGU/86NS/KYK4O7UT/FGU86NSKYK4O7UT.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Affix the Add-on Straps to the Device.' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Insert the fishing line loop into the hole in the robot push button device's arm and then peel off the double-stick tape film and carefully attach it to rocker arm. But first try this without removing the tape's film to test the best location while operating the function via your smartphone's SmartBot app. When satisfied secure it and then proceed to the next step.</li></ol>",
