g?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F07/KUI1/KYK4O7V6/F07KUI1KYK4O7V6.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FRV/C1F8/KYK4O7VL/FRVC1F8KYK4O7VL.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FT9/J66Y/KYK4O7VI/FT9J66YKYK4O7VI.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/F7V/7Z4Q/KYK4O7VM/F7V7Z4QKYK4O7VM.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure><figure><img src='https://content.instructables.com/FGG/M820/KYK4O7VC/FGGM820KYK4O7VC.jpg?auto=webp&fit=bounds&frame=1&height=1024&width=1024auto=webp&frame=1&height=300&auto=webp&fit=bounds&width=600&height=450&quality=75' alt='Open App and Remotely Operate Your Screen/bot.' loading='lazy'></figure></div><p><strong>Étapes :</strong></p><ol><li>Open the app on your smartphone and initialize the robot push button device via bluetooth. And then acquaint yourself with which button is ON and OFF for LOWER and RAISE. If you get the SwitchBot Mini Hub you can contol this with your voice via Alexa SmartHome and other services.</li><li>Enjoy,</li><li>E.D.M.</li><li>to my generous patrons</li></ol>",
